msgid "A trash can."
msgstr "ゴミ箱。"

msgid "Some black goo can be seen at the bottom."
msgstr "底に黒いべとべとしたものが見える。"

msgid "A pile of trash cans."
msgstr "ゴミ箱の山。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Ending_K7_2.misc_trashcans.dlg.narrator"
msgid "They seem to be stuck together."
msgstr "お互いにくっつけられているようだ。"

msgid "So... maybe the ritual worked?"
msgstr "じゃあ……もしかして儀式が成功したってこと？"

msgid "But the ritual wasn't finished."
msgstr "でもまだ儀式は終わってない。"

msgid "Which means either the school has a bunch of cursed-looking rooms and a dark secret, or this isn't the school anymore."
msgstr "つまり、この学校に無数の呪われてそうな部屋と何らかの暗い秘密があるか、それともここがもう学校じゃないか、そのどちらかね。"

msgid "If it's not the school, then what is it?"
msgstr "ここが学校じゃないなら一体何なの？"

msgid "No idea."
msgstr "さあね。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Ending_K7_2.move_enter.dlg.prologue_girl1"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "In any case, it doesn't feel too dangerous, so let's continue."
msgstr "いずれにしても、そんなに危険な感じはしないし、先へ進みましょう。"
